articles.author: Sydney Borchers
articles.title: First 'virgin birth' found in American crocodile as reptile spends 16 years in isolation - Fox News
articles.description: The first-ever recorded documentation of a crocodile's "virgin birth" has been released in a recent study after an isolated crocodile in Costa Rica laid 14 eggs.
articles.content:
The first-known occurrence of a "virgin birth" by a crocodile has been documented by scientists, according to a study published by on Wednesday Biology Letters, a peer-reviewed journal.
